    "MissionGiver": "Citizens for Prosperity",
    "Title": "Gather Supplies Across Outpost",
    "Description": "Hi, \n\nWe\u2019re a little shorthanded at one of our outposts and could use some help. We need someone to gather supplies spread across a few buildings and bring them to one spot.\n\nHere\u2019s what needs to be gathered:\n\nPick up package <EM4>#~mission(Item1|SerialNumber)</EM4> at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>.\nPick up package <EM4>#~mission(Item4|SerialNumber)</EM4> at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>.\nPick up package <EM4>#~mission(Item5|SerialNumber)</EM4> at <EM4>~mission(Location1|Address)</EM4>.\nPick up package <EM4>#~mission(Item2|SerialNumber)</EM4> at <EM4>~mission(Location1|Address)</EM4>.\nPick up package <EM4>#~mission(Item3|SerialNumber)</EM4> at <EM4>~mission(Location2|Address)</EM4>.\n  \nEach one needs to end up at <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4>. Simple enough, right?\n\nAlso, to make your life easier, I'd make sure you have a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> with you. \n \nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
    "DisplayDescription": "Hi, \n\nWe\u2019re a little shorthanded at one of our outposts and could use some help. We need someone to gather supplies spread across a few buildings and bring them to one spot.\n\nHere\u2019s what needs to be gathered:\n\nPick up package <EM4>#[Item1|SerialNumber]</EM4> at <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4>.\nPick up package <EM4>#[Item4|SerialNumber]</EM4> at <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4>.\nPick up package <EM4>#[Item5|SerialNumber]</EM4> at <EM4>[Location1|Address]</EM4>.\nPick up package <EM4>#[Item2|SerialNumber]</EM4> at <EM4>[Location1|Address]</EM4>.\nPick up package <EM4>#[Item3|SerialNumber]</EM4> at <EM4>[Location2|Address]</EM4>.\n  \nEach one needs to end up at <EM4>[Destination|Address]</EM4>. Simple enough, right?\n\nAlso, to make your life easier, I'd make sure you have a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> with you. \n \nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
